description: Discover a haven of luxury and tranquility in this exquisite 2-bedroom, 2.5-bath plus home office residence. With floor-to-ceiling windows that flood the space with natural light and offer spectacular views, this home boasts a refined ambiance complemented by soaring 10-foot ceilings. Residence 1906 features a chef’s dream kitchen, elegantly outfitted with custom gray-gloss Italian cabinetry, gleaming quartz countertops, and top-of-the-line Thermador appliances, making it perfect for hosting and entertaining. Offering an additional home office with the option to be enclosed by sleek, opaque glass sliding doors for added privacy. The opulent primary suite includes a spacious en suite bathroom adorned with marble flooring and a bespoke walk-in closet, while the second bedroom also benefits from its own en suite bathroom. Further enhanced by Lutron motorized window treatments, custom-built closets, a custom-built Murphy bed, 40 square feet of private storage and 2 valet parking spots.
